Some days I work from a tiny Airbnb, other days I‚Äôm on a night bus heading somewhere new.

I work as a designer, share content about this lifestyle, and recently started a podcast called Out of Office Club. üòäüéôÔ∏è

It‚Äôs where I talk about the real side of travel and remote work. Not just the sunsets and wifi caf√©s, but the doubts, the burnout, and the little moments that make it all worth it.
